{"tid":1858182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢男子身患肺炎，得不到醫院救治，不想傳染妻兒而跳橋自殺","createTime":"2020-02-02T14:17:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T17:43:15.000Z","uid":313615,"like":47,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"9ec65ea7a071672e62544442076e9afc5483f36d","tid":1858182,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T14:17:12.000Z","msg":"2月2號，大陸資深媒體人曹山石twitter披露咗武漢冠狀病毒感染患者自殺嘅悲劇故事。<br />\n<br />\n事發2月1號傍晚5點半，壹個感染新型冠狀病毒嘅武漢男子喺橋上跳落自殺。佢喺自殺前喊，好sad，好絕望，寂靜嘅街道，佢出盡力聲，心底刺痛。<br />\n男子畀感染咗冠狀病毒，屋企唔留咗，驚感染傳畀老婆同個仔，但醫院冇床位，佢借屋住。佢想去睇醫生，冇車，要行好遠好遠嘅路，佢體力已經唔夠，而家佢肚餓，生不如死。<br />\n目擊者感嘆，&ldquo;男子縱身越過，了卻咗世間所有恩怨。&rdquo;目擊者報警，嚟咗架潛行獸，差佬叮囑話唔好喺網上發布消息，目擊者聽後&ldquo;自己含淚笑咗&rdquo;。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/02/02/221700_7be992ac6d99136100ea9852a1b10b95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F02%2F02%2F221700_7be992ac6d99136100ea9852a1b10b95.jpg&h=a3b57b75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b1808937c865d06ce15f707530a91c0ed3a3088","tid":1858182,"uid":199816,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T14:18:23.000Z","msg":"支持香港醫護<br />\n聽日一齊罷工好唔好？"},{"pid":"3315a6202d0480107983a79a76290ea601842d80","tid":1858182,"uid":224857,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T14:19:52.000Z","msg":"來生不要做中國人了"},{"pid":"a64b6ea7b9d50b778ab205ecfb80488911fab064","tid":1858182,"uid":126621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T14:19:56.000Z","msg":"好似biohazard d 劇情<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2129110ff422e8d8643839d278a57e07729ad68a","tid":1858182,"uid":192409,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T14:20:20.000Z","msg":"醫院無位<br />\n屋企唔敢返<br />\n又病又驚又餓<br />\n突然間覺得真係好慘"},{"pid":"e633909cdfdd793256b9d583a65f86ed2ecdad59","tid":1858182,"uid":126621,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T14:20:47.000Z","msg":"